[CII Startup Members & Select Non-Members]

CII CIES Masterclass on Corporate Venture Capital (CVC)
From Capital to Catalyst: Building Tomorrow’s Business Through CVC

11 December 2025 (Thursday)| 09:30 AM – 1:05 PM | Virtual Platform

CII CIES and CII Western Region Startup Committee are organizing an online half day Masterclass on CVC with the theme:  “From Capital to Catalyst: Building Tomorrow’s Business Through CVC”  on 11 December 2025 from 0930 – 1305 hrs over virtual Platform.

This half-day masterclass brings together industry leaders and innovation experts to explore how CVCs are driving growth, accelerating startup collaborations, and shaping the next era of corporate innovation.

Who Should Attend


	Corporate Strategy, Innovation & Investment Leaders
	Venture Capital & PE Professionals
	Startup Founders & Ecosystem Enablers
	Academia & Innovation Policy Professionals


Register Here: https://cam.mycii.in/ORNew/Registration.html?EventId=E000072244

We look forward to your participation in this insightful session designed to decode how CVC can become a catalyst for building tomorrow’s businesses.

/Secretary

N M P Jeyesh
Senior Director & Head Startups
CII Centre of Excellence for Innovation, Entrepreneurship & Startups (CII CIES)
Confederation of Indian Industry
6th Floor, T-Hub 2.0 20, Inorbit Mall Road
Vittal Rao Nagar Madhapur
Hyderabad Telangana 500081
W: www.cii.in ; www.ciicies.in  
Note:

Startup and Corporate Members are requested to make a note of the following to ensure receipt of various startup-related communication from CII:


	 All startup-related emails from CII are normally issued from the email ID noreply@ciiiconnalpha.in with the display name 'CII Startup'. Members are requested to add this email ID to their contact and safe sender lists to ensure all emails from this email domain get delivered to their respective inboxes.
	CII has also launched a dedicated mobile app “CII Alpha” which is available on Google Play Store and iOS App Store. Information regarding Startup initiatives of CII is published on the App regularly. Users of CII Alpha App can also connect, engage, and network with other users from corporates and the startup ecosystem. Download links of the app are given below:

	To receive important communication through SMS or WhatsApp, members are requested to install and update their profiles with mobile numbers in the profile section of the CII Alpha App.
